summary:
I'm a graphic designer specialized in social media, typography, illustration and lettering. I'm also a great fan of film photography and handmade illustration like papercut and watercolour painting, that's what I do in my free time.
My objective as a designer is to get into new universes and expressive languages, where I can put to work my skills and my personal style. 
You can discover what I do in: https://flocatalano.myportfolio.com/
